com.thomsonreuters.ema.access

Interface OmmArrayEntry


  • public interface OmmArrayEntry
    OmmArrayEntry represents an entry of OmmArray.

    OmmArrayEntry associates entry's data and its data type.

    • Method Detail

      • loadType

        int loadType()
        Returns the DataType of the entry's load. Return of DataType.DataTypes.ERROR signifies error while extracting content of load.
        Returns:
        data type of the contained object

      • code

        int code()
        Returns the Code of the entry's load. The code indicates a special state of a Data. Attempts to extract data will cause OmmInvalidUsageException if Data.DataCode.BLANK is returned.
        Returns:
        data code of the contained object
